OL,3,CEnergy price cap could rise by #16 to
OL,4,Chelp suppliers cover customer debts
OL,6,FThe UK's energy watchdog has said it
OL,7,Fwill lift the energy price cap from
OL,8,FApril next year to help suppliers
OL,9,Frecover almost #3 billion in debts
OL,10,Ffrom customers who cannot pay their
OL,11,Fbills.
OL,13,FThe one-off price cap adjustment will
OL,14,Fadd up to #16, which will increase gas
OL,15,Fbills by around #1.33 a month on
OL,16,Faverage, Ofgem said.
OL,18,FThe watchdog said energy companies
OL,19,Fshould use the extra money to support
OL,20,Fstruggling customers and to write off
OL,21,Fbad debts.
